originalText.text:
The studio is thoughtfully designed with an infinity cove cyc. A great outdoor space for a breath of fresh air or outdoor lunch. A separate hair and makeup area with a skylight. Great selection in the cafe. Top level customer service.

For those seeking a top-notch studio in midtown, this place is a must-see.

originalText.text:
This is a rare find in midtown New York an amazingly new photo studio that is a perfect size perfect location in perfect setup.  Operating 24 hours a day with the ground floor walk-in super convenient super clean. There's also a area to pull up parking unload right in front so no worries about lugging your gear all over the place.

The space is nicely laid out and has a cute Cafe area offering a variety of coffee, tea and beverages.

The studio even has a small outdoor space to grab some fresh air as well as an amazing HAIR and MU area with a great skylight.

Definitely worth looking into if you're looking for something in the midtown area.

originalText.text: I used to hate shooting here bc it’s so far away. But now I love it, need it, eat it, breathe it, live for it. The intimate setting and the private patio and make up room add a unique on set charm. The workers are absolutely incredible. Aidan, Liam, Yan and Luca all deliver exceptional service. I would recommend this studio for anyone looking for an authentic New York fashion studio experience. I love it here forever and always.
